  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed across five flow-speed combinations. Thirteen credibility factors are assessed; the package decision is recorded as Accepted on the basis of overall engineering judgment, although structured level data reveal that several factors — most notably Discretization error and Model form — carry achievedLevel values strictly below their requiredLevel thresholds.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cou2-hemolysis-absolute",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cou2-cfd-hemolysis-vad",
